getReason() - Method in class dev.blue.brawl.events.PlayerEliminateEvent
Returns the reason for the death.
If no reason was set in the PlayerCombatEvent, it will return the most recent DamageCause.
If the player died to the Void after taking damage from a different cause, this will return as follows:

DAMAGE_CAUSE$VOID

This allows you to split at '$', allowing you to determine who caused them to die to the void.
